    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have to see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such incredible care of it, and it's in absolutely flawless condition inside and out. It drives like a total dream and looks even better in person. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been pampered and is ready for a new home, this is definitely the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions at all!",
