    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2010 Porsche 911 Carrera S, a definitive example of the 997.2 generation. This vehicle features the 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), delivering 385 hp through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The mechanical synchronization is flawless, with the factory-optioned Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) providing exceptional damping control and chassis rigidity. Every component, from the cross-drilled rotors and four-piston monobloc calipers to the meticulously maintained cooling system, remains in peak operational status. The underside is free of corrosion, and the engine exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders. This is a turn-key investment for the purist seeking uncompromised longitudinal and lateral performance.",
